Attempting to add more animations to UINavigationController, just trying ideas, any input is welcome.

To use import the .h

#import "UINavigationController+animatedNavController.h"

And then call

[self.navigationController pushWithAnim:detailViewController inView:self.view];


or

[self.navigationController pushWithAnim:detailViewController inView:self.view withAnchor:CGPointMake(x,y)];


to pop a view call

[self.navigationController shrinkLastViewController];